    .container-fluid
      h1.mt-4 Lunch For 4
      h6
      p
        | Welcome to the Aurora University Social Committee's Lunch For 4 Application! This is the Users Home Page.
      p
        | If there is no sidebar, it can be accessed by clicking on the "Toggle Menu" button at the top left.
      p
        | Here is what you can do here:
      h3 Editing your Info-
      p  Has something changed? Do you want to change your email? last name? Click on the side tab "Edit Info" to change your first name, last name, department, or email. You email must still remain an Aurora University email.
      h3 Check Participation Status-
      p
        | Click on the "status" tab in the left sidebar to check your participation status or change it. Participation status means that you have the option to be in an 'active' or 'suspended' state. By selecting 'active' you will be automatically assigned to meetings and notified of 
        | details. If you are in the 'suspended' state, that means you have opted not to participate in meetings at the moment and will not be assigned to any. You can select your status by selecting the desired checkbox. The status page will also indicate if you have been selected as a leader for the next meeting.
      h3 Leader Options-
      p
        | If you are a leader, the leader tab will appear on the left. If you are not a leader, then it will not be there. In the leader tab you have options to edit the current meeting. You can change the date, location, and comments for the meeting.
        | You can also submit whether the meeting is pending, if it did meet, or if it did not.
      h3 Log Out-
      p The log out button is located on the left sidebar will securely log you out of the application and redirect you to the login page.
      img(src='https://athletics.aurora.edu/images/logos/site/site.png' id='image' alt='Aurora University Logo' style='width:100px; height:100px;')
      
